# Manjaro

## Install
1. Download the furus
2. Select the image method of DD
3. Install the Manjaro

## config
### Input Method
4. Do:sudo pacman -Sy fcitx-im fcitx-configtool fcitx-googlepinyin
5. Do:sudo nano ~/.xprofile

   export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx

   export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx

   export XMODIFIERS="@im=fcitx"
6. Do:sudo pacman -Sy wqy-microhei

### Tool
7. Do:sudo pacman -Sy yaourt
8. Do:yaourt -S atom
9. Do:yaourt -S visual-studio-code-bin

### Desktop

10. Set the bottom bar panel unclock and then move it to the top
